fy_waterwars - by Me0w
______________________

This is my first map ever. I think it's good. Do I care what you think? ;D

__________________________________________________

Notes :

-
-buy zone is the middle island, just like you would expect for an fy map ;D.
-all players spawn with a knife only, then you can pick up guns on the islands
-in the beginning of each round, it may lag because the weapons fall from the air all together - but after those 2 seconds (approx) it won't lag anymore.
